<th colspan="2" style="text-align:center; font-size:larger;" class="fn summary">Richard Scarry</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<th>Born</th>
<td>June 5, 1919<span style="display:none">(<span class="bday">1919-06-05</span>)</span><br />
